<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1436,1828,2036]" box="[199,1136,1863,1892]" pageId="6" pageNumber="209">Abdominal apodemes small and broad, extending to posterior margin of 3rd sternite.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1436,1828,2036]" pageId="6" pageNumber="209">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,381,1902,1927]" pageId="6" pageNumber="209">Male genitalia:</emphasis>
Pygofer with about 2 macrosetae at cephalo-ventral angle of lobe (
<figureCitation box="[1164,1248,1902,1927]" captionStart="FIGURE 5" captionStartId="7.[151,250,1947,1969]" captionTargetBox="[183,1416,339,1891]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[151,1436,301,1934]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURE 5. Anufrievia curva Yang &amp; Zhang sp. nov. a. genital capsule; b. pygofer dorsal appendage, lateral view; c. pygofer dorsal appendage, posterior view; d. style; e. apex of style; f. aedeagus, ventral view; g. aedeagus, lateral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1444108/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="209">Fig. 5a</figureCitation>
); apex of dorsal appendage bifurcated, scissor-shaped (
<figureCitation box="[581,694,1939,1964]" captionStart="FIGURE 5" captionStartId="7.[151,250,1947,1969]" captionTargetBox="[183,1416,339,1891]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[151,1436,301,1934]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURE 5. Anufrievia curva Yang &amp; Zhang sp. nov. a. genital capsule; b. pygofer dorsal appendage, lateral view; c. pygofer dorsal appendage, posterior view; d. style; e. apex of style; f. aedeagus, ventral view; g. aedeagus, lateral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1444108/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="209">Figs 5b, c</figureCitation>
). Style with apical tooth curved, longer than subapical tooth, inner margin of subapical tooth serrated (
<figureCitation box="[567,689,1974,1999]" captionStart="FIGURE 5" captionStartId="7.[151,250,1947,1969]" captionTargetBox="[183,1416,339,1891]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[151,1436,301,1934]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURE 5. Anufrievia curva Yang &amp; Zhang sp. nov. a. genital capsule; b. pygofer dorsal appendage, lateral view; c. pygofer dorsal appendage, posterior view; d. style; e. apex of style; f. aedeagus, ventral view; g. aedeagus, lateral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1444108/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="209">Figs 5d, e</figureCitation>
). Aedeagal shaft with pair of apical processes moderately long; preatrial process long, apex truncated, surpassing gonopore; gonopore central (
<figureCitation box="[1034,1144,2011,2036]" captionStart="FIGURE 5" captionStartId="7.[151,250,1947,1969]" captionTargetBox="[183,1416,339,1891]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[151,1436,301,1934]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURE 5. Anufrievia curva Yang &amp; Zhang sp. nov. a. genital capsule; b. pygofer dorsal appendage, lateral view; c. pygofer dorsal appendage, posterior view; d. style; e. apex of style; f. aedeagus, ventral view; g. aedeagus, lateral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1444108/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="209">Figs 5f, g</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
